{"tid":849052,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"葡萄牙宣布今年唔要C朗","createTime":"2018-10-05T11:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T12:22:53.000Z","uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c41df78c96fc90a60443633b7e1d49910f3c606","tid":849052,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181005/photo/bkn-20181005120355468-1005_00882_001_01p.jpg?20181005141013\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181005120355468-1005_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20181005141013&h=026fa055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙周五公布新一期國家隊大軍名單，<span style=\"color: red;\">被控強姦</span>嘅王牌球星C朗拿度名落孫山。葡萄牙領隊費蘭度山度士講到C朗嘅話題，就以「私人事件」為由避談涉嫌強姦事件，但佢表示同葡萄牙足總主席商討完後，決定今年內都唔會再召C朗拿度入國家隊。費蘭度山度士表示：「未來2次嘅國家隊點兵，即係今次同下個月，C朗都唔會入選，我哋同意暫時唔搵佢代表國家隊。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，葡萄牙上個月點兵出戰歐洲國家聯賽，C朗拿度已經獲准免役休息，不過今次繼續唔選佢之餘，仲提早講定下次點兵都冇C朗份，似乎好有「割席」嘅味道。"},{"pid":"48c6b98c75005b60588ce1eb20fd2ad26c0a5798","tid":849052,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"我相信牙朗係無辜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e2d0126db835cb2e97320e63a95a427fff41ad","tid":849052,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:48:26.000Z","msg":"ac華係時候上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5de147cbb093e7baf09a5a2d020d04e29f56619","tid":849052,"uid":213709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892da17e55dee740c9a3983c8ef73ed9b1c7fff9","tid":849052,"uid":168924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"強姦犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}